  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The army is called in large numbers to Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the army has been called in large numbers near the Prime Minister's office in Malpara, Colombo. Videos showing how the army is coming to those areas are currently being shared on social media networks.",
        "Apart from this, there is also a video showing how a helicopter belonging to the Air Force is flying above Gallumudoora and the Prime Minister's Office."
      ],
